infopoint-html (1:0.2.0.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * new upstream version
  * add AUTOSTART config and set AUTOSTART="no" in /etc/default
  * add default page that is displayed if no URL is configured in
    /etc/default/ or given on the command line
  * finished init script
    - start on first available X display
    - write PID to pidfile
    - implemented stop, restart, force-reload
    - send xinit output to logfile
  * set empty URL in /etc/default so the instruction page is shown on 
    first start
  * only delete user on purge; otherwise dpkg --purge would try to 
    delete the user twice, and complain
  * tidy up xulrunner updates on purge

 -- Roland Hieber <rohieb@rohieb.name>  Thu, 17 Mar 2011 06:42:13 +0100

infopoint-html (1:0.1.0.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * renamed vertretungsplan-anzeige to infopoint-html
  * ported to xulrunner version, no Firefox or Iceweasel needed
  * changed Maintainer to Roland Hieber <rohieb@rohieb.name>
  * a cron rule to stop the system is not part of this package anymore

 -- Roland Hieber <rohieb@rohieb.name>  Fri, 11 Mar 2011 05:07:14 +0100
